body:
The amount for the purposes of paragraph 6(1)(c) of Schedule 1 in respect of a family of which at least one member is a child or young person—
is £20.22 in respect of a reduction week which begins in the period beginning with 1st April 2016 and ending with 30th April 2016;
is nil in respect of a reduction week which begins after 1st May 2016.
